2026-05-13T17:44:47.2848392Z 242        <!--
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2848806Z 243            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2849155Z 244            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2849495Z 245            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2849860Z 246            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2850093Z 247            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2850492Z 248            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2850840Z 249            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2881498Z 250            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2881908Z 251            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2882097Z 252        -->
2026-05-13T17:44:47.2882269Z 253        <activity
